{"tid":1904054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「武漢肺炎」 逾千患者一半無發燒 .........","createTime":"2020-02-29T11:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T11:50:00.000Z","uid":123335,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e650528b9c251245d6f8f93a97b7044b322d6d","tid":1904054,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKx02uv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKx02uv.jpg&h=50cb4fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中文大學醫學院內科及藥物治療學系系主任許樹昌早前聯同多名專家，分析了內地30個省份，合共逾1000名確診者資料，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">結果發現僅有43.8%患者在入院時有發燒，即使住院期間也只有88.7%人有發燒，即很多患者沒有出現發燒的情況</span></strong>，而約一半患者的肺部電腦掃描顯示有磨玻璃樣班塊（ground-glass opacity)，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但亦有一成八患者在放射診斷下完全沒有異常情況。</span></strong><br />\n (Source: hk01)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">痴撚線病毒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bcddc2317817617429d2cde366291a4cd2c80d74","tid":1904054,"uid":291357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有排帶口罩"},{"pid":"0652d6c22d9a0a0e25e679f6eb542d415ae2a7fb","tid":1904054,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcddc2317817617429d2cde366291a4cd2c80d74","tid":1904054,"uid":291357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有排帶口罩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:25:02.000Z","msg":"都唔知有冇隱形帶病者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a681cd7ea370a968a7d88cff493885b32d0b1418","tid":1904054,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:27:27.000Z","msg":"咁講實際上有咩傷害<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor